## 8. Animation Easing

### 8.1 Easing Functions

```typescript
// Ease-out cubic: starts fast, decelerates (navigation)
function easeOutCubic(t: number): number {
  return 1 - Math.pow(1 - t, 3);
}

// Ease-in-out cubic: smooth start and end (zoom)
function easeInOutCubic(t: number): number {
  return t < 0.5
    ? 4 * t * t * t
    : 1 - Math.pow(-2 * t + 2, 3) / 2;
}

// Ease-out expo: fast deceleration (inertia)
function easeOutExpo(t: number): number {
  return t === 1 ? 1 : 1 - Math.pow(2, -10 * t);
}
```

### 8.2 Animation Durations

| Animation Type | Duration | Easing |
|----------------|----------|--------|
| Zoom (animated) | 250ms | easeInOutCubic |
| Pan (inertia) | 300-500ms | easeOutExpo |
| LOD crossfade | 200ms | smoothstep |
| Navigation jump | 300ms | easeOutCubic |
| Tooltip fade | 150ms | linear |

